   <body>
      <context>
         <p>To create programs from an agreement, perform the following steps:</p>
      </context>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Log in to the Customer Incentive Manager and click <image placement="inline"
                      width="35"
                      href="../attachments/102432691/107118605.jpg"/> on the Home page.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Go to <uicontrol>Contract Lifecycle Management </uicontrol>and then click <uicontrol>Agreement.</uicontrol>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click<uicontrol> New Agreement </uicontrol>to create an agreement.</p>
            <p>
               <p>
                  <fig>
                     <image placement="break"
                            width="499"
                            href="../attachments/102432691/107118603.jpg"/>
                  </fig>The New Agreement - Select Agreement Record Type page appears as follows:</p>
               <p>
                  <fig>
                     <image height="250"
                            placement="break"
                            width="696"
                            href="../attachments/102432691/108499843.png"/>
                  </fig>
               </p>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Select any one of the record types.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>Continue</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Fill the mandatory information such as Agreement Name, Account, Start Date, and End Date.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>Save</uicontrol>. </p>
            <p>
               <p>The new agreement is created.</p>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>After the agreement is created, click <uicontrol>New Program </uicontrol>to create a program.</p>
            <p>
               <fig>
                  <image placement="break"
                         width="500"
                         href="../attachments/102432691/107118600.png"/>
               </fig>
            </p>
         </li>
      </ol>
   </body>
